items: Duke of vrbin . a weake Lord of a selfe admiring wisedome .
An honorable learned ladie companion to the princesse Dulcimel .
A vertuous , faire wittie Lady , his wife .
brother to Sir Amoroso and a vitious bragart .
A yong courtier , & a common louer .
A poore laundresse of the court that washeth and diets footemen .
